# 3D Printer for Christmas

## Summary

This chirstmas, I want to gift my family and friends something unusual: I want to 3D print my gifts!

## Plan

Yes, I know, at this point building a 3D printer is almost a cliche (is it?!), but this is my first hardware project. I'll follow these steps:

I'll first do a 3D design the printer using Inventor. Then I will cut the body of the printer out of wood pieces. I'll then set up the components and the driver code.

